for a mini-hook of his own. ; Photo, COLOR, Kareem Abdul-Jabbar, in vintage 
form, shoots over Seattle's Xavier McDaniel for two of the 16 points he scored 
in 28 minutes. AL SEIB / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
